thread.title: Tim Collins

author: Tim Collins
title: Tim Collins
text:
The manager, Destinee, made my transition to the new StorageMart ownership painless with her usual efficiency, competence, and professionalism -- all, over the phone! Thanks Destinee!
This location (on Wharncliffe South in London ON) is clean, safe, secure, and well-managed. I have an indoor locker and I have never had a problem with access or cart availability.
And no cigarette smoke (I'm allergic to it, so I'd notice!) or crackheads, either! :)
As another reviewer stated, you get what you pay for.
